          {
            "text": "To provide a system and method for accurately finding the pose of a 3D model in a 3D image of an object acquired by a 3D camera assembly.SOLUTION: A method for finding the pose of a 3D model in a 3D image of an object acquired by a 3D camera assembly comprises the steps of: providing the 3D model to a vision system processor; providing the acquired 3D image to the vision system processor; and finding, with the processor, a pose that matches 3D edges in the 3D model to 3D edges in the 3D image and matches 3D normals in the 3D model to 3D normals in the 3D image simultaneously.SELECTED DRAWING: Figure 2",
            "lang": "en"
          }
